      <title>保加利亚将取消俄罗斯汽油税，着眼于申根</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bulgaria-to-drop-russian-gas-tax-with-eye-on-schengen-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚执政联盟计划取消对俄罗斯天然气通过其领土过境的有争议的税收，因为这个巴尔干国家寻求改善与欧盟国家的关系并加入申根免签证旅行区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bulgaria-to-drop-russian-gas-tax-with-eye-on-schengen-access</guid>
